description: One of the latest show models to leave Mobile Space System's design office, this time to demonstrate that MSS could do solid work even on a budget, the Pi packs a lot of power into a very compact hull with two pods of five thrusters each. It has found modest success among the somewhat-wealthy who are looking for an affordable way to show off.
